Q5:  Client Server model is usually used in a big network and for big tasks but peer to peer network is used for small tasks like printing
Peer to Peer model is usually faster to Client Server model as they are closer and require lesser time to send the document 
Peer to Peer is easier to set up but have no centralised device unlike Client Server where there is a centralised device but harder to set up 
It is more costly to set up CLient Server model as compared to Peer to Peer model. 
